<td><font face="Arial,Helvetica">0.318701523</font></td>
</tr>
</table>

<p><b><font face="Arial,Helvetica">Hence, multiplying together the P(IBS=2)
for each locus gives:</font></b>
<table BORDER WIDTH="480" >
